text:
🧿🔔🎛️🪜Located at a less visited corner of the Park, and adjacent to the Dog Run, Sense Discovery Garden is a space with an array of displays showcasing the five human senses of sight, sound, touch, smell and perhaps taste..
🎭Some of the display structures were found broken (spoilt).
⏰The entire Sense Discovery Garden may probably be due for a revamp.
I am not sure which one is the Sense Discovery
